dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is William Griffin. May I please have your name?
Hi, my name is Julia Butler.
Nice to meet you, Julia. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is five six two three four and my date of birth is zero four dash one zero dash one nine eight five.
Thank you, Julia. I also need the make and model of the vehicle involved in the incident and the location where it occurred.
The vehicle is a two zero one eight Honda Civic and the incident happened on Main Street near the park.
Thank you for providing that information, Julia. We will start processing your claim. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Julia. Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
